  "attributes": {
    "about_this_biz_specialties": "Gastelum Tree Service is a family-owned, locally operated tree service business in Vacaville, CA, established in 1991. We specialize in tree trimming, tree removal, hazardous tree removal, stump grinding, emergency tree service, mistletoe tree removal, and landscaping services. Our team brings decades of experience and is dedicated to delivering safe, efficient, and affordable tree services in Vacaville, CA. Whether you need routine maintenance or storm damage tree removal in Vacaville, CA, we offer competitive rates and superior customer service. As a small business, we take pride in serving our community with integrity and care. Get in touch with us today and let us handle your tree care needs.",
    "about_this_biz_year_established": "1991",
